skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my composter
des: My Composter allows users to learn how to compost through a step by step guide. It also allows users to learn about certain ingredients used in compost and how to speed up to composting process. In addition, the Alexa Skill can give users interesting facts about composting.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
